<div class='mailer__content'>
  <p class='govuk-body'>Dear <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>

  <p class='govuk-body'>Thank you for participating in our CPD and choosing to
    start your learning journey with Teach Computing. We just wanted to let you
    know that in doing so, you have already taken a big step towards achieving
    our national training certificate in GCSE computer science.</p>

  <p class='govuk-body'><strong>About the Computer Science Accelerator Programme</strong></p>

  <p class='govuk-body'>Our professional development programme will help you to
    develop the subject knowledge to teach GCSE computer science, whatever your
    background or career stage.
    <br>We have a wide range of courses for you to choose from, available online
    and through live remote delivery. You can select the areas where you need
    the most support, and tailor the amount of training you do to suit your
    needs.</p>

  <p class='govuk-body'>
    <%= link_to 'Browse our courses', courses_url(certificate: @programme.slug), class: 'govuk-button button' %>
  </p>

<p class='govuk-body'><strong>Next steps</strong></p>

  <p class='govuk-body'>
    Take your next steps towards certification, by simply enrolling on the
    programme. It's free to join and will provide you with immediate access to
    your own personal dashboard, enabling you to track your progress towards
    completing the programme.
  </p>

  <p class='govuk-body'>
    <%= link_to 'Enrol for free', cs_accelerator_url, class: 'govuk-button button' %>
  </p>

  <p class='govuk-body'><strong>Need more information?</strong></p>

  <p class='govuk-body'>If you would like more information about the programme
    or your next steps, contact our
    <%= mail_to 'CSChampionSupport@stem.org.uk', 'Computer Science Champions', class: 'ncce-link' %>
    for guidance and support.
  </p>
</div>
